# LiNKaios Foundation

## What This Repo Is

LiNKaios is the AI Operating System (AIOS) control plane for the LiNKtrend Venture Factory. It coordinates how missions are created, decomposed, assigned, approved, and completed across all agents, while enforcing identity, permissions, tenant boundaries, and policy guardrails.

Canonical spec: `docs/AIOS_MASTER_SPEC.md`

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Monorepo | Turborepo + pnpm |
| Language (orchestration) | TypeScript / Node.js |
| Language (workers) | Python (uv-managed) |
| Memory plane | Supabase (Postgres + pgvector) |
| Inter-agent transport | NATS (JetStream) |
| Automation | n8n (LiNKautowork) |
| Orchestration | Paperclip |
| Management agents | OpenClaw |
| Execution agents | Agent Zero |
| Embedding model | nomic-embed-text (768 dims) via Ollama on Mac Mini |

## Workspace Layout

```
apps/
  LiNKaios/          # Control plane web UI (Next.js App Router)
  LiNKautowork/      # n8n workflow assets and automation configs
packages/
  linkbrain/          # LiNKbrain SQL schemas, RPC layer, memory utilities
  linklogic/          # Shared logic and contract types
  linkskills/         # Skill module interfaces and registry
linkbots/
  internal/           # Manager and worker persona runtime skeletons
applets/
  link-paperclip/     # Orchestration core (git submodule → link-paperclip)
  link-openclaw/      # Manager agent framework (git submodule → link-openclaw)
  link-agent-zero/    # Worker agent framework (git submodule → link-agent-zero)
  link-llm-council/   # LLM Council / Board of Advisors (git submodule → link-llm-council)
infra/
  debian-vps/         # VPS Docker Compose, bootstrap, deploy scripts
  droplet-admin/      # DigitalOcean droplet with Caddy reverse proxy
  mac-mini/           # Mac Mini config (Ollama, execution node)
docs/                 # Cross-thread product and engineering specs
scripts/              # Bootstrap, validation, acceptance harness scripts
```

## Package Manager

- **pnpm** with workspaces.
- Add workspace-level deps with `pnpm add <dep> -w`.
- Add app/package-specific deps with `pnpm add <dep> -F <filter>`.
- Keep `package.json` scripts as the primary orchestration interface.

## Architecture Separation

LiNKaios coordinates multiple planes without collapsing their boundaries:

| Plane | System | Boundary |
|-------|--------|----------|
| Orchestration | Paperclip | Scheduling, hierarchy, heartbeat |
| Management | OpenClaw | Planning, governance, delegation |
| Execution | Agent Zero | Code, CLI, terminal operations |
| Logic | LiNKskills | Reusable governed skill modules |
| Memory | LiNKbrain | Persistent state, audit, retrieval |
| Automation | LiNKautowork | Deterministic workflow execution |

Do not write code that collapses these boundaries. Each plane has its own responsibility. Scheduling logic stays in orchestration. Planning logic stays in management. Implementation stays in execution.
